reviewText: One of Dolph Lundgen's better movies
Other great movie from the 1980's Dolph Lundren and Jean-Claude Van Damme at there best!
Great movie despite reviews! If you're an 80s action film person than this is a must watch. Dolph and Claude kill in this action packed thriller.
The Holy Buns of Van Damme make a glorious appearance, worship them for they have been oiled and glistening! :D
Great movie! One of my favorites from the 90's. Van Damme and Lundgren were awesome together on screen. I highly recommend this scifi/action movie.
A very well made and awesome movie for it's time.
